# Maps (Leaflet)

- Follow patterns in `MapWrapper`, `LeafletMap`, and `leafletFix.ts` when changing map behavior.
- Avoid importing Leaflet on the server unless the existing pattern already does; respect client-only boundaries so SSR does not touch `window` or Leaflet globals.
